## Shop Fix Cycle 02 Screen Evidence Pending

Status: `WIP_FIXING_PENDING_DEPLOY`

Target public screen:

- `https://shop.aiboux.com/s/aiboux/admin`

Required visible-value check:

- The public admin screen must not show the fixed demo values reported by the user.
- Checks must use public URL curl and public URL Playwright rendered DOM.

Pre-deploy observation:

- Public curl with no-cache headers returned HTTP 200 and did not find the reported fixed values in HTML.
- Public Playwright rendered DOM returned HTTP 200 and did not show the reported fixed values in visible text.
- A Shop AI assistant source component still contained fixed Shop sample values; that source has been changed to `未集計` / `0件` before deploy.
- A Global AI assistant placeholder included a person-name example that caused `佐藤` to appear in rendered HTML, even though it was not visible text. That placeholder now uses a generic `取引先` example.

This evidence is WIP and not FINAL_ACCEPTED.

