- The public TOP page uses the tenant URL `https://shop.aiboux.com/s/aiboux/`.
- The public TOP page keeps the Shop service root separate from the tenant storefront.
- The public TOP page renders an Amazon-like header, category navigation, hero area, and product sections.
- The product detail page renders an Amazon-like product detail structure with image gallery, product information, and purchase box.

